file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Swagger Petstore
  description: 'This is a sample server Petstore server.'
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: https://petstore.swagger.io/v2
paths:
  /pets:
    post:
      summary: Add pets
      operationId: addPets
      requestBody:
        content:
          text/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pet'
      responses:
        200:
          description: successful operation
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
components:
  schemas:
    Pet:
      type: object
      properties:
        Name:
          type: string

Error: notImplemented: path "/pets": post: requestBody: contents: unsupported content types: [text/json]
